WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:24.020 --> 01:24.890
There's something

01:25.810 --> 01:27.060
that was quite peculiar.

01:28.180 --> 01:30.300
Our department received a pack of cash.

01:30.380 --> 01:32.700
It was designated
as payment for Tan Qianqian's bill.

01:33.300 --> 01:34.570
Yet we don't know who sent it.

01:39.940 --> 01:40.740
Ms. Fang,

01:41.850 --> 01:43.170
I came to meet you...

01:45.050 --> 01:46.170
Don't tell your dad.

01:46.170 --> 01:46.650
Yes.

01:46.650 --> 01:47.810
I know.

01:47.810 --> 01:48.490
Hmm.

01:53.100 --> 01:53.780
Ming Sheng.

01:55.300 --> 01:57.770
You're a lot like your dad.

02:20.980 --> 02:29.680
[Episode 18]
["I Forgot My Umbrella" Was a Lie]

02:37.420 --> 02:38.470
You didn't bring an umbrella?

02:42.910 --> 02:43.940
No.

02:45.140 --> 02:45.940
What about you?

02:48.670 --> 02:49.470
Me neither.

02:53.500 --> 02:54.829
How have you been?

02:58.030 --> 02:59.270
Pretty good.

02:59.670 --> 03:01.830
I'm in the top 50 in the grade ranking,

03:01.910 --> 03:03.110
and I have made new friends.

03:04.190 --> 03:04.990
What about you?

03:06.700 --> 03:08.500
I heard about your dad's incident.

03:11.340 --> 03:12.550
It's just a medical dispute.

03:12.830 --> 03:14.190
It's common.

03:14.630 --> 03:15.470
It's not a big deal.

03:18.030 --> 03:18.910
Good to know that.

03:22.700 --> 03:23.910
- You...
- You...

03:29.750 --> 03:32.700
I'm planning to apply for medical school
at the University of Paris,

03:33.630 --> 03:35.390
so I'll be focusing

03:35.940 --> 03:37.140
on preparing for studying abroad.

03:37.950 --> 03:41.070
I might have to leave school.

03:45.670 --> 03:47.390
Today might be the last time we meet.

03:48.550 --> 03:50.829
Don't you have anything to say to me?

03:58.420 --> 03:59.700
I wish you the best of luck.

04:10.300 --> 04:11.790
The rain's easing off. I got to go.

04:11.790 --> 04:12.790
Hold on.

04:20.620 --> 04:21.620
I said I didn't bring an umbrella.

04:23.350 --> 04:24.300
It was a lie.

04:31.860 --> 04:33.580
Since this is the last time we meet

04:33.700 --> 04:35.350
and I can't return it to you after this,

04:35.620 --> 04:36.700
I'm not taking it.

05:12.550 --> 05:13.620
What's wrong with you?

05:14.460 --> 05:15.990
You're always so clueless.

05:16.180 --> 05:17.740
Think before you act.

05:17.900 --> 05:19.990
I don't know what's on your mind.

05:26.740 --> 05:27.550
Yes.

05:27.740 --> 05:29.140
Mumu and you are good friends.

05:29.550 --> 05:31.550
Her dad is sick,
so you should visit him.

05:31.790 --> 05:33.550
Going once is fine,

05:34.140 --> 05:35.700
but you keep going.

05:36.860 --> 05:37.790
That's a hospital.

05:38.790 --> 05:40.860
Can't you spend more time
on your studies?

05:43.470 --> 05:44.909
I feel bad for Mumu.

05:45.470 --> 05:47.110
Her dad got sick

05:47.620 --> 05:49.550
right before the NCEE,

05:50.470 --> 05:52.030
which has affected his child.

05:56.860 --> 06:00.500
Mom, how much is life worth?

06:00.790 --> 06:02.500
One hundred thousand,
two hundred thousand,

06:02.590 --> 06:03.620
or three hundred thousand?

06:03.940 --> 06:05.710
Or does every life
have a different price?

06:06.860 --> 06:08.740
How much do you think my life is worth?

06:09.030 --> 06:10.740
And what about Qiao Beiyu's life?

06:19.260 --> 06:20.150
Two years ago,

06:20.150 --> 06:21.790
when I came to Huanzhou
to deliver your clothes,

06:21.790 --> 06:23.060
I ran into Qiao Beiyu.

06:26.230 --> 06:27.470
She said this to me at that time.

06:29.150 --> 06:31.300
I'll give them back to you, okay?

06:33.030 --> 06:34.670
Was that

06:34.820 --> 06:36.909
when she realized
her family had abandoned her?

06:42.300 --> 06:43.500
Take it while it's hot.

06:44.260 --> 06:45.300
Rest up early.

07:55.380 --> 07:56.110
Mom.

07:57.260 --> 07:58.820
What are you doing up here?

08:38.549 --> 08:40.470
The meal's ready.

08:40.789 --> 08:42.059
I'll send you to school later.

08:44.670 --> 08:45.470
Where's Mom?

08:47.990 --> 08:49.940
Something came up at the noodle house,

08:50.740 --> 08:51.790
so she had to leave.

08:52.940 --> 08:53.740
Dad.

08:54.350 --> 08:56.500
Don't you think
Mom's been acting strangely?

08:56.990 --> 08:58.180
Last night,

08:58.180 --> 09:00.110
I saw her standing alone on the rooftop.

09:00.110 --> 09:01.350
It looked like she was sleepwalking.

09:02.710 --> 09:03.670
Nonsense.

09:03.670 --> 09:06.230
She's getting older,

09:06.230 --> 09:07.260
going through menopause,

09:07.300 --> 09:08.740
and having trouble sleeping.

09:08.860 --> 09:09.990
It's not the first time.

09:09.990 --> 09:11.420
It happened once in Nanqiao Village.

09:11.910 --> 09:12.860
That's enough.

09:13.740 --> 09:15.790
Don't over-think.

09:15.940 --> 09:17.790
Come on, or you'll be late for school.

09:19.500 --> 09:20.300
Eat up.

09:36.210 --> 09:41.440
[Huanzhou High School]

09:50.110 --> 09:50.910
These days,

09:51.820 --> 09:53.940
I keep dreaming
about things from my childhood.

09:56.950 --> 09:59.780
Dad treated me quite well
when I was a kid.

10:01.020 --> 10:02.430
He would make me delicious food,

10:02.590 --> 10:03.740
read me stories,

10:04.070 --> 10:06.660
and even let me ride on his shoulders
at the lantern festival.

10:08.310 --> 10:10.470
Dad, Mom, and I.

10:10.740 --> 10:13.260
The three of us
were always so happy together.

10:16.070 --> 10:16.900
I think

10:19.900 --> 10:21.950
Mom still remembers all that.

10:22.230 --> 10:23.260
That's why

10:23.900 --> 10:25.740
she's put up with him all these years.

10:31.710 --> 10:32.540
Well,

10:32.540 --> 10:33.380
back then,

10:34.260 --> 10:36.140
Dad was a math teacher

10:36.140 --> 10:37.310
at Huanzhou No.1 Experimental
Elementary School.

10:37.660 --> 10:39.990
He used to be charming and funny.

10:40.590 --> 10:42.540
He was always awarded
as the Excellent Teacher.

10:42.780 --> 10:44.500
All the students liked him very much.

10:47.140 --> 10:48.260
Until that time

10:48.740 --> 10:51.110
when one of my kindergarten classmates
had a birthday party.

10:53.620 --> 10:56.190
It was my first time
going to a birthday party.

10:57.990 --> 10:59.350
When I think about that now,

11:00.310 --> 11:03.860
everything that happened that day
felt like a fairy tale.

11:07.110 --> 11:08.710
I'd never seen

11:09.350 --> 11:11.020
such a beautiful princess gown

11:11.380 --> 11:13.620
or tasted such delicious ice cream.

11:15.140 --> 11:17.900
After I got home,
I kept bothering my dad.

11:17.900 --> 11:20.430
I said, "Dad!

11:23.350 --> 11:24.950
I also want a big house

11:26.430 --> 11:28.190
and beautiful clothes.

11:29.350 --> 11:33.110
Why isn't our family as rich as others?"

11:38.990 --> 11:41.350
Qingyu, do you think

11:41.620 --> 11:43.830
my dad quit his job as a teacher

11:43.990 --> 11:46.260
and started a business

11:46.990 --> 11:48.350
because of what I said?

11:50.830 --> 11:52.380
If it weren't for me,

11:52.830 --> 11:54.620
he wouldn't have experienced
business failure,

11:54.710 --> 11:56.110
taken out high-interest loans,

11:56.860 --> 11:58.070
started drinking,

11:59.430 --> 12:01.660
and ended up like this.

12:05.590 --> 12:08.350
No. That's just your guess.

12:11.740 --> 12:13.230
What if it's true?

12:23.990 --> 12:26.830
Mumu, listen.

12:26.830 --> 12:29.310
No one can easily change others' fate.

12:29.660 --> 12:32.230
Please don't punish yourself
for what someone else did.

12:49.350 --> 12:51.230
Dribble the ball, and it'll pass.
Try it.

12:54.380 --> 12:55.430
See?

12:55.500 --> 12:56.830
I told you not to dribble the ball.

12:57.810 --> 12:59.110
[Tan Qianqian's husband]

13:06.710 --> 13:08.020
Good.

13:14.830 --> 13:16.260
Sheng, you called us

13:16.260 --> 13:17.710
to play basketball
in the middle of the day,

13:18.140 --> 13:19.110
and yet you're sitting here alone.

13:19.110 --> 13:19.900
What are you reading?

13:22.070 --> 13:22.990
Still trying to figure something out?

13:23.020 --> 13:23.830
Well.

13:25.230 --> 13:27.380
I have a feeling
that the money the hospital received

13:27.710 --> 13:29.500
has something to do
with the patient's husband.

13:29.990 --> 13:31.380
I found his house's phone number,

13:32.190 --> 13:33.470
but they won't say anything.

13:34.470 --> 13:35.620
This is strange.

13:35.950 --> 13:37.430
They paid the bill,

13:37.430 --> 13:38.990
yet they're also demanding money
for compensation.

13:39.380 --> 13:40.380
How contradictory.

13:40.660 --> 13:42.070
You even found the family's number.

13:42.470 --> 13:43.260
That's easy.

13:43.660 --> 13:44.470
Call me Mr. Lin,

13:44.470 --> 13:45.660
and I'll help you.

13:46.590 --> 13:47.380
Mr. Lin.

13:48.620 --> 13:49.710
Heh.

13:59.230 --> 14:01.660
All right. I'll take note of it.

14:18.950 --> 14:20.100
[Huanzhou Association]
We hold volunteer activities

14:20.100 --> 14:21.190
[of AIDS Prevention and Control]
every Saturday.

14:21.190 --> 14:22.230
You're always welcome there.

14:29.110 --> 14:30.590
What?

14:30.780 --> 14:32.190
Do you want my pocket money?

14:33.470 --> 14:35.380
Of course I do,

14:35.710 --> 14:36.990
but what are you up to again?

14:37.230 --> 14:38.110
Do me a favor.

14:46.840 --> 14:53.360
[Huanzhou Association of STDs
and AIDS Prevention and Control]

15:21.660 --> 15:22.310
Hello.

15:23.660 --> 15:24.860
Hello, I'm Fangfang.

15:24.860 --> 15:25.950
I'm a volunteer here.

15:25.950 --> 15:26.830
What's your name?

15:27.110 --> 15:28.230
I'm Qiao Qingyu.

15:28.350 --> 15:29.430
Qiao Qingyu.

15:29.620 --> 15:30.830
I'll call you Qingyu.

15:30.900 --> 15:32.350
Is this your first time here, Qingyu?

15:34.620 --> 15:35.740
You don't have to feel shy.

15:35.860 --> 15:37.900
Everyone came here to seek help.

15:37.900 --> 15:39.430
Admitting you need help

15:39.430 --> 15:41.190
is the first step toward healing.

15:41.350 --> 15:42.540
You've got it wrong.

15:42.540 --> 15:43.990
I'm not...

15:44.020 --> 15:44.780
Don't worry.

15:44.780 --> 15:46.310
We will never disclose the identities

15:46.310 --> 15:47.500
of those who seek help here.

15:51.020 --> 15:51.660
Fangfang.

15:53.140 --> 15:54.430
Qingyu is my student.

15:59.830 --> 16:00.310
Come.

16:01.260 --> 16:02.990
We are a voluntary
professional social organization

16:02.990 --> 16:05.430
formed by AIDS prevention workers

16:05.430 --> 16:08.190
and concerned individuals.

16:08.350 --> 16:09.780
We serve as a bridge

16:09.780 --> 16:11.660
between the government and social forces

16:11.660 --> 16:12.780
on AIDS prevention.

16:13.620 --> 16:14.350
Currently,

16:14.350 --> 16:16.070
our registered volunteers

16:16.070 --> 16:17.590
are over 130.

16:17.660 --> 16:19.380
They all have their own jobs.

16:19.470 --> 16:21.070
Even so, they make time

16:21.310 --> 16:22.830
to travel to various places nationwide

16:22.830 --> 16:24.710
for HIV prevention events.

16:25.660 --> 16:28.020
At the same, we also
provide counseling services

16:28.020 --> 16:29.470
for individuals exposed to HIV

16:29.540 --> 16:31.950
to help reduce their risk of infection.

16:32.780 --> 16:33.470
Aside from that,

16:33.470 --> 16:34.860
we hold public awareness talks

16:34.860 --> 16:37.070
on AIDS prevention every Saturday.

16:37.230 --> 16:37.620
Come with me.

16:37.860 --> 16:40.310
AIDS is a chronic disease.

16:40.780 --> 16:42.900
If left untreated

16:43.140 --> 16:45.590
after infection,

16:46.020 --> 16:48.660
the patient's life expectancy
is usually around ten years.

16:48.990 --> 16:51.590
[AIDS Knowledge Lecture]
Untreated symptoms

16:51.950 --> 16:53.190
can be fatal

16:53.190 --> 16:55.230
within 12 and 18 months.

16:55.660 --> 16:56.620
AIDS

16:56.620 --> 16:58.430
is a highly contagious
and dangerous disease

16:58.860 --> 17:00.620
triggered by HIV.

17:00.950 --> 17:02.830
HIV attacks

17:02.830 --> 17:04.380
the human immune system.

17:09.380 --> 17:10.369
[Huanzhou Association of STDs and AIDS]
Thank you so much,

17:10.369 --> 17:10.990
[Prevention and Control]
Dr. Zhang.

17:11.589 --> 17:12.380
Don't mention it.

17:12.780 --> 17:14.660
This is Dr. Zhang Xiaohui,
an infectologist.

17:14.660 --> 17:15.260
Like me,

17:15.260 --> 17:16.990
he's also a volunteer here.

17:17.109 --> 17:18.710
This is my student, Qiao Qingyu.

17:18.710 --> 17:19.500
Hello.

17:19.859 --> 17:22.109
Qingyu has some questions
she'd like to ask you about.

17:22.380 --> 17:23.380
I'll leave you two to it.

17:23.380 --> 17:24.020
Sure.

17:26.859 --> 17:27.950
Dr. Zhang,

17:28.430 --> 17:31.310
if a patient's infection
is detected early

17:31.470 --> 17:33.540
and they take medication properly
during the early stage,

17:34.070 --> 17:35.430
what might cause their condition

17:35.430 --> 17:37.350
to worsen so quickly

17:37.500 --> 17:38.860
or even lead to death

17:38.990 --> 17:40.140
in a short period of time?

17:41.740 --> 17:42.900
Generally,

17:43.260 --> 17:45.190
patients in such conditions

17:45.190 --> 17:46.500
will have their life expectancy
greatly extended.

17:47.190 --> 17:49.140
The possibility of sudden death is low.

17:50.230 --> 17:52.430
I think the patient's death

17:52.430 --> 17:54.070
might be due to other reasons.

17:55.740 --> 17:58.830
Are you suggesting
they didn't die of AIDS?

18:03.860 --> 18:04.660
Hey, you're back.

18:05.900 --> 18:08.860
Hmm. I'm back
to fetch some clean clothes.

18:09.190 --> 18:11.710
I see. Is that your dirty laundry
in the bag?

18:12.020 --> 18:13.950
Leave them here. I'll wash them for you.

18:14.900 --> 18:16.110
Are you brushing its fur?

18:16.110 --> 18:18.020
Yeah, giving it a good grooming.

18:18.380 --> 18:19.230
I noticed

18:19.230 --> 18:21.020
you're more patient with this dog

18:21.020 --> 18:23.430
than you were with me when I was little.

18:23.590 --> 18:26.190
Do you know why?

18:26.780 --> 18:28.340
Because it's cuter than you.

18:28.470 --> 18:28.990
Sch.

18:32.580 --> 18:33.540
I heard

18:34.670 --> 18:38.230
the mediation is set for next week.

18:39.340 --> 18:42.230
Yes. Don't worry about that.

18:42.910 --> 18:44.390
Your priority now

18:44.390 --> 18:45.390
is to focus on your studies

18:45.390 --> 18:46.820
and pass the TEF.

18:47.190 --> 18:48.950
I couldn't care less about that.

18:51.710 --> 18:52.500
Do you regret it?

18:52.990 --> 18:53.950
Regret what?

18:54.740 --> 18:55.870
Treating that patient.

18:58.870 --> 18:59.870
I don't regret it.

19:00.340 --> 19:03.020
If it happened again,

19:03.540 --> 19:05.390
I'd do the same thing.

19:13.260 --> 19:15.500
Did you buy this for the dog?

19:16.870 --> 19:18.430
Of course.

19:19.820 --> 19:20.990
It's a pretty dog,

19:20.990 --> 19:22.060
but your taste...

19:23.230 --> 19:23.990
It's ugly.

19:24.390 --> 19:27.540
Doggy, my dad says
you're cuter than me,

19:28.430 --> 19:29.020
do you agree?

19:33.670 --> 19:35.630
Gosh, so smelly.

19:35.950 --> 19:37.390
Give it to me.

19:37.500 --> 19:38.230
Give it to me.

20:28.780 --> 20:30.630
Why aren't you back yet, Mom?

20:31.020 --> 20:32.150
Qingyu, it's me.

20:32.340 --> 20:33.630
Mom's in the hospital!

20:33.950 --> 20:34.580
What?

20:35.820 --> 20:38.260
You'd better take turns
to look after her tonight

20:38.390 --> 20:40.990
in case anything happens.

20:41.430 --> 20:42.990
Dad, what's going on?

20:43.100 --> 20:44.300
Why is Mom suddenly sick?

20:44.630 --> 20:46.630
The patient

20:46.670 --> 20:47.630
is stable now.

20:47.780 --> 20:49.540
The main reason she fainted

20:49.580 --> 20:51.390
is because she took too much Paroxetine.

20:51.820 --> 20:54.340
Keep a close eye on her,

20:54.630 --> 20:56.780
especially her medication dosage.

20:56.820 --> 20:58.020
What's Paroxetine?

20:58.020 --> 20:59.580
Why is she taking it?

21:00.430 --> 21:02.540
You don't know?

21:02.780 --> 21:05.100
Paroxetine is an antidepressant.

21:05.470 --> 21:07.300
The patient has depression.

21:08.540 --> 21:09.710
I brought you the medicine.

21:09.740 --> 21:10.540
Take them on time.

21:10.540 --> 21:11.020
All right.

21:11.020 --> 21:12.540
Don't let your injuries act up again.

21:13.150 --> 21:14.230
I know.

21:16.540 --> 21:17.340
Depression...

22:07.430 --> 22:08.020
Dad.

22:10.780 --> 22:11.820
Did you know Mom's condition

22:11.820 --> 22:13.540
all along?

22:25.870 --> 22:28.020
Actually, the painkiller bottle

22:28.580 --> 22:30.060
[Painkiller]
had Paroxetine in it.

22:30.990 --> 22:32.300
It's an antidepressant.

22:34.740 --> 22:36.950
Remember her shoulder pain?

22:37.630 --> 22:39.430
It's triggered by depression.

22:41.470 --> 22:42.710
When did this happen?

22:46.500 --> 22:50.230
I think it was not long
after Bei's death.

22:53.710 --> 22:55.500
It was just after the Lantern Festival.

22:56.340 --> 22:58.060
Yu and you were still in Shunyun.

23:00.500 --> 23:02.740
So we brought Bei's ashes

23:04.230 --> 23:05.580
back to Nanqiao Village.

23:24.710 --> 23:25.780
Beiyu.

23:31.020 --> 23:33.580
Do you hate me and your dad?

23:35.190 --> 23:36.470
If my parents

23:37.230 --> 23:39.470
had

23:40.470 --> 23:42.020
new children

23:43.990 --> 23:45.950
and left me

23:48.950 --> 23:51.100
with my grandparents,

23:51.820 --> 23:52.990
I'd feel

23:53.100 --> 23:56.260
abandoned and unloved.

23:56.580 --> 23:57.150
Right?

23:58.710 --> 24:00.870
"If I wasn't important,

24:00.870 --> 24:04.340
nothing I said or did

24:04.580 --> 24:06.150
would matter

24:08.910 --> 24:10.820
to them."

24:11.780 --> 24:13.630
Were you thinking this way?

24:13.630 --> 24:14.950
Get some sleep.

24:24.780 --> 24:26.390
She's gone.

24:26.390 --> 24:28.190
Stop dwelling on it, Fanghao.

24:29.670 --> 24:31.100
We need to pull ourselves together.

24:32.780 --> 24:34.990
We still have Qingyu and Yu.

24:36.780 --> 24:39.540
Our life needs to carry on.

24:41.190 --> 24:42.740
Get a grip.

24:49.910 --> 24:50.950
Go to sleep, all right?

24:53.190 --> 24:55.950
At first, Dad and Mom didn't allow Beiyu
to be buried in the family tomb.

24:56.950 --> 24:58.340
Haisheng and I

24:58.740 --> 25:00.300
tried so hard to convince them,

25:01.500 --> 25:02.740
and eventually, they agreed.

25:04.260 --> 25:05.470
But Dad said

25:06.470 --> 25:07.780
she could be buried in the family tomb

25:09.430 --> 25:10.910
without a gravestone.

25:11.670 --> 25:12.500
Exactly.

25:13.820 --> 25:15.540
People would laugh at us
if we set a gravestone for her.

25:15.630 --> 25:16.430
Quiet.

26:22.630 --> 26:23.670
Fanghao!

26:30.100 --> 26:31.190
Fanghao!

26:38.390 --> 26:39.230
Fanghao!

26:42.340 --> 26:43.300
Fanghao!

26:52.990 --> 26:53.710
Fanghao.

26:59.580 --> 27:00.260
Why are you doing here

27:00.260 --> 27:01.390
in the middle of the night?

27:02.340 --> 27:03.150
Get up.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.020
Get up now.

27:09.260 --> 27:10.150
You'll catch a cold.

27:10.300 --> 27:10.820
Quick.

27:14.100 --> 27:14.670
What's wrong with you?

27:14.670 --> 27:16.670
What are you doing? I want to sleep.

27:16.670 --> 27:18.020
Let go of me.

27:18.870 --> 27:20.020
Stop it, okay?

27:20.470 --> 27:21.670
Bei's gone.

27:21.670 --> 27:22.670
She's dead.

27:22.740 --> 27:23.540
It's cold here.

27:27.630 --> 27:28.870
Let's go home, all right?

27:30.150 --> 27:32.500
Can't you let me rest for a bit?

27:59.300 --> 28:01.430
I noticed something was wrong
with her at that time.

28:02.710 --> 28:03.910
After returning to Shunyun,

28:04.870 --> 28:06.340
I took her to the hospital.

28:17.820 --> 28:18.540
Madam,

28:18.670 --> 28:20.430
the doctor has something
to say to your husband.

28:20.430 --> 28:21.780
I'll take you to collect the medicine.

28:21.870 --> 28:22.670
Follow me.

28:26.950 --> 28:27.740
Your wife

28:27.740 --> 28:29.950
has mild depression.

28:30.020 --> 28:32.430
[Psychiatry Clinic Room (1)]
The symptoms include low mood,

28:32.430 --> 28:34.780
self-doubt, self-blame,
psychomotor retardation,

28:35.340 --> 28:37.060
anhedonia,

28:37.300 --> 28:38.500
fatigue, and more.

28:39.470 --> 28:41.990
Sometimes, it also shows

28:41.990 --> 28:43.300
somatic symptoms,

28:43.300 --> 28:46.430
such as sleep disturbances, weight loss,

28:46.540 --> 28:48.060
and body pain.

28:48.390 --> 28:49.740
As her family,

28:50.100 --> 28:52.500
aside from making sure
she takes medication on time,

28:52.780 --> 28:54.950
you need to accept

28:54.950 --> 28:56.300
her behaviors and emotions.

28:56.430 --> 28:57.470
Be there for her.

28:57.740 --> 28:59.190
Don't blame

28:59.390 --> 29:00.470
or upset her.

29:00.710 --> 29:02.630
Give advice or encouragement.

29:03.150 --> 29:04.910
Depression is an illness.

29:05.230 --> 29:08.060
Family support and understanding
matter a lot.

29:08.190 --> 29:08.950
Do you understand?

29:08.950 --> 29:09.580
Yes.

29:10.500 --> 29:12.470
All right. I'll prepare a list of things

29:12.470 --> 29:13.580
you need to keep in mind.

29:13.630 --> 29:14.910
Remember to follow them at home.

29:16.990 --> 29:18.190
Your mom doesn't like
to show her weakness

29:18.540 --> 29:19.950
or worry you.

29:20.630 --> 29:21.470
So

29:21.740 --> 29:23.430
just pretend you don't know about this.

29:55.470 --> 29:56.430
Hi, mister.

29:57.260 --> 29:58.820
Is this your first visit?

29:58.820 --> 29:59.630
Yes.

30:00.500 --> 30:02.190
Are you here to go sightseeing

30:02.190 --> 30:03.630
or visit relatives?

30:04.670 --> 30:05.470
Neither.

30:05.710 --> 30:06.780
I came here to look for someone.

30:06.950 --> 30:07.910
Alone?

30:08.150 --> 30:10.950
Whoa, young people these days
are something else.

30:18.100 --> 30:20.340
Are you sure this is the right place?

30:20.910 --> 30:22.190
Could it be a mistake?

30:23.780 --> 30:24.820
Yes, it's here.

30:34.910 --> 30:36.190
Sir, you can stop here.

30:36.190 --> 30:36.820
Okay.

30:42.020 --> 30:42.670
Thank you.

30:43.630 --> 30:45.710
Be careful, young man.

30:45.780 --> 30:47.150
Okay. Thank you.

30:53.190 --> 30:54.060
Excuse me.

30:55.060 --> 30:55.780
Who are you looking for?

30:56.990 --> 30:58.300
I'm looking for this person.

30:58.340 --> 31:01.020
Could you take a look if he's here?

31:06.470 --> 31:07.100
He's over there.

31:07.230 --> 31:08.190
I'll take you to him.

31:08.390 --> 31:09.190
Thank you.

31:13.780 --> 31:14.910
Come here.

31:18.990 --> 31:19.780
Thank you.

31:28.190 --> 31:29.780
Hello, I'm Ming Sheng.

31:30.020 --> 31:32.500
I'm the son of Ming Qiuxin
from Huanzhou People's Hospital.

31:33.290 --> 31:37.610
[Huanzhou People's Mediation Committee
for Medical Disputes]

31:49.500 --> 31:51.430
The mediator and the patient's family
have arrived.

31:53.990 --> 31:55.020
What do you need me to do?

31:57.060 --> 31:58.870
I hope you can give the patient's family

31:59.780 --> 32:01.430
a brief apology

32:01.430 --> 32:04.190
during the mediation later.

32:05.670 --> 32:07.950
I've prepared a draft of it.

32:08.390 --> 32:09.190
Please have a look.

32:20.950 --> 32:23.260
As matters stand,

32:24.150 --> 32:26.780
unless the family
withdraws the complaint

32:26.780 --> 32:28.390
and apologizes to us,

32:28.740 --> 32:31.990
Dr. Ming will be affected.

32:32.260 --> 32:35.430
We'll try to minimize the damage.

32:37.470 --> 32:37.870
Okay.

32:38.630 --> 32:39.950
Understood.

32:41.260 --> 32:42.260
It's almost time.

32:42.260 --> 32:43.190
Let's go in.

32:44.020 --> 32:44.540
All right.

32:50.390 --> 32:52.230
Dr. Ming.

32:54.150 --> 32:55.230
Tan Qianqian's husband?

32:56.630 --> 32:58.430
Dr. Ming, I...

32:59.300 --> 33:00.190
I'm so sorry.

33:03.780 --> 33:07.670
When we came from the county
to Huanzhou,

33:07.990 --> 33:10.060
no hospital was willing
to take my wife in.

33:10.820 --> 33:12.820
They all told us to go home
and wait for the time.

33:13.340 --> 33:16.340
But only you took the risk

33:16.950 --> 33:18.670
and gave us hope.

33:20.390 --> 33:22.630
Before the surgery, my wife said to me,

33:23.740 --> 33:25.260
no matter what happens,

33:25.500 --> 33:27.230
you'll always be our savior.

33:29.820 --> 33:31.190
After she passed away,

33:31.470 --> 33:32.870
I couldn't pay the medical bill.

33:33.540 --> 33:34.820
I was so embarrassed

33:35.670 --> 33:37.260
that I snuck off to find a job,

33:37.710 --> 33:39.430
hoping to pay the bill off
as soon as I could.

33:40.630 --> 33:41.300
I...

33:42.300 --> 33:43.670
I didn't know

33:43.670 --> 33:45.470
my family would do something like this.

33:45.990 --> 33:47.300
I may not be well-educated,

33:48.150 --> 33:48.950
but I know

33:48.950 --> 33:50.990
I shouldn't bite the hand that feeds.

33:52.150 --> 33:54.540
So don't worry, Dr. Ming.

33:54.910 --> 33:57.390
I came here to withdraw the complaint.

33:58.230 --> 33:59.910
I won't let you suffer this unfairness.

34:24.870 --> 34:26.340
Your French teacher told me

34:26.949 --> 34:28.949
you haven't been to class for days.

34:37.710 --> 34:39.389
I already know
everything they're teaching.

34:39.389 --> 34:40.340
I don't want to go.

34:43.710 --> 34:45.780
I thought you went
to look for the patient's family.

34:46.909 --> 34:47.949
You knew about that?

34:51.540 --> 34:53.429
Thank you, Sheng.

34:54.389 --> 34:55.389
Don't thank me.

34:56.739 --> 34:58.020
I don't need that from you.

34:59.780 --> 35:01.190
I have to thank you.

35:05.260 --> 35:06.500
How did you know about this place?

35:09.060 --> 35:11.190
You used to run away here
after arguments with Grandpa

35:11.190 --> 35:12.230
when you were little, remember?

35:12.910 --> 35:14.500
You slept under this banyan tree.

35:15.780 --> 35:17.340
I carried you home after that.

35:19.630 --> 35:21.390
I thought it was Grandpa.

35:22.190 --> 35:23.780
Why didn't you tell me about this?

35:33.790 --> 35:37.310
You've been a troublesome kid
since you were little.

35:37.870 --> 35:39.270
You always make us worry.

35:39.270 --> 35:40.310
That's rich coming from you.

35:41.100 --> 35:42.910
Since I was a kid, you've always
been out early and home late.

35:42.910 --> 35:44.020
I couldn't even see you.

35:44.060 --> 35:45.270
I didn't have a chance
to make you worry.

35:49.140 --> 35:53.100
There was once
I had been in surgery all day.

35:54.020 --> 35:56.060
I was so exhausted
that I could barely stand up straight.

35:56.100 --> 35:57.430
All I wanted was to go home
and lie down.

35:58.060 --> 36:00.100
But when I lifted the blanket,

36:01.470 --> 36:03.870
I found instant noodles
spread all over the bed.

36:05.020 --> 36:06.500
I was so furious

36:06.700 --> 36:07.830
that I decided

36:08.220 --> 36:10.350
to punish you for not watching cartoons
for a whole month.

36:11.870 --> 36:13.750
Your crying was so loud.

36:13.910 --> 36:15.270
It was like it could shake the earth.

36:15.500 --> 36:16.660
Do you remember this?

36:23.870 --> 36:25.060
Of course I do.

36:26.540 --> 36:27.750
You got off work very late that day.

36:28.750 --> 36:29.830
I was worried you might be hungry,

36:30.750 --> 36:32.220
so I prepared
the last instant noodle we had

36:32.220 --> 36:33.100
for you.

36:33.750 --> 36:34.660
I was waiting for you,

36:36.060 --> 36:37.750
but you hadn't come back

36:37.750 --> 36:38.870
even though I was about to fall asleep.

36:40.060 --> 36:41.350
I was worried
the noodles would get cold,

36:42.270 --> 36:44.990
so I kept them in the blanket
to keep them warm.

36:47.430 --> 36:48.540
I cried

36:49.350 --> 36:50.660
not because I was angry.

36:52.620 --> 36:54.140
I just felt so wronged.

37:02.180 --> 37:02.870
You've never

37:05.100 --> 37:06.700
told me about that.

37:11.790 --> 37:13.020
It's not too late to say it now.

37:13.430 --> 37:14.060
Hmm.

37:17.390 --> 37:18.500
It's not too late.

37:33.430 --> 37:35.270
Hey, did you hear

37:35.270 --> 37:37.140
about Ming Sheng's dad's
medical dispute?

37:37.140 --> 37:38.790
Not only did the patient's family
withdraw the complaint,

37:38.790 --> 37:39.990
but they also issued an apology
in the newspapers.

37:40.180 --> 37:41.950
Seriously? What a twist.

37:43.060 --> 37:44.660
Qingyu, since you're close
to Ming Sheng,

37:44.660 --> 37:45.990
do you know anything about it?

37:47.390 --> 37:48.990
I'm not that close to him.

37:51.140 --> 37:53.220
Come on. It's pretty clear

37:53.220 --> 37:55.430
there's more to his feelings
for you than just a classmate's.

37:57.350 --> 37:58.620
Why aren't you...

37:59.270 --> 38:00.470
Angry?

38:03.020 --> 38:04.870
Guess what?

38:04.870 --> 38:06.390
I've got a brand new goal.

38:06.390 --> 38:07.950
Now, I just want to focus on my studies.

38:07.950 --> 38:08.430
Sch.

38:08.620 --> 38:10.540
I bet you won't last
more than six months.

38:11.180 --> 38:13.100
Let's go to the library, Qingyu.

38:13.140 --> 38:14.580
Maybe next time.
I need to be somewhere else.

38:16.700 --> 38:18.140
"Maybe next time.
I need to be somewhere else."

38:18.140 --> 38:18.750
Let's go ourselves.

38:30.590 --> 38:33.440
[Huanzhou Association of STDs and AIDS Prevention and Control]

38:40.310 --> 38:41.660
Talk about perfect timing, Qingyu.

38:41.750 --> 38:43.870
I need you to sign this form
for our records.

38:44.020 --> 38:44.620
All right.

38:46.160 --> 38:49.060
[Applicant's signature: Qiao Qingyu]

38:50.430 --> 38:51.100
It's done.

38:52.060 --> 38:52.990
From now on,

38:52.990 --> 38:55.020
you're a member of our association.

38:55.020 --> 38:56.060
Welcome aboard, Qiao Qingyu.

38:56.060 --> 38:58.710
[Volunteer ID: Qiao Qingyu]

38:59.220 --> 39:00.350
We've been working on

39:00.350 --> 39:02.220
the displaying of our aid events.

39:02.220 --> 39:03.470
The caption is already ready.

39:03.470 --> 39:05.140
These are the volunteers' photos

39:05.140 --> 39:06.060
during the past year's events.

39:06.140 --> 39:07.430
Find a suitable caption

39:07.430 --> 39:08.580
and paste it on them.

39:08.580 --> 39:09.310
Sure.

39:09.430 --> 39:10.750
I'll get back to work.

39:53.140 --> 39:53.950
Actually,

39:55.220 --> 39:57.310
when I saw your name in the school,

39:57.790 --> 39:58.750
I was wondering

39:59.270 --> 40:01.180
if you were Qiao Beiyu's sister.

40:02.830 --> 40:05.220
Do you know Qiao Beiyu, Ms. Le Fan?

40:08.100 --> 40:10.430
We always have AIDS prevention campaigns
at the association.

40:10.910 --> 40:13.310
That's how Beiyu and I met.

40:14.180 --> 40:15.470
Whenever we had events,

40:15.470 --> 40:16.700
Beiyu would always show up.

40:16.700 --> 40:17.660
Dr. Le Fan.

40:18.830 --> 40:19.390
Glad to see you here, Beiyu.

40:19.390 --> 40:19.790
Hmm.

40:19.990 --> 40:21.180
Just a moment.

40:21.830 --> 40:23.060
Every time, she'd come along,

40:23.060 --> 40:24.470
doing everything she could to help.

40:24.870 --> 40:25.830
Until that day...

40:25.830 --> 40:26.620
Hello?

40:27.350 --> 40:28.350
Is this Qiao Beiyu?

40:28.790 --> 40:31.220
It's been a while. Have you missed me?

40:31.540 --> 40:33.310
I'll be waiting for you
at our spot tonight.

40:41.310 --> 40:42.180
Dr. Le Fan,

40:43.390 --> 40:44.580
I need to go.

40:47.540 --> 40:50.910
Before long, I heard she passed.

40:53.790 --> 40:55.140
I've always wondered

40:55.750 --> 40:57.390
if I hadn't stopped her that day,

40:59.470 --> 41:01.220
would things
have turned out differently?

41:03.790 --> 41:04.750
Ms. Le Fan,

41:05.580 --> 41:07.660
do you know how Qiao Beiyu died?

41:17.430 --> 41:19.060
You know what? It caught us off guard.

41:19.220 --> 41:20.100
At noon,

41:20.100 --> 41:21.990
Grandpa and Grandma called,

41:21.990 --> 41:23.500
saying they wanted us to go back.

41:23.660 --> 41:25.660
They also mentioned that they knew
Dad and Mom had been through a lot.

41:27.020 --> 41:28.220
Since we're family,

41:28.220 --> 41:29.310
they'd let the past go.

41:29.830 --> 41:31.100
Qiao Qingyu,

41:31.430 --> 41:33.950
this is it.

41:34.140 --> 41:35.020
I quit.

41:35.310 --> 41:36.910
I'm done covering for you.

41:38.140 --> 41:40.060
No matter how much
pocket money you give me.

41:40.500 --> 41:41.620
Those peanuts

41:41.830 --> 41:43.660
aren't enough to compensate
for my emotional distress.

41:45.390 --> 41:46.750
Qiao Beiyu didn't die of the disease.

41:47.100 --> 41:47.910
She committed suicide.

42:20.550 --> 42:24.240
♪Perhaps♪

42:24.750 --> 42:30.450
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:31.590 --> 42:36.990
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:37.990 --> 42:43.550
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:49.220 --> 42:52.890
♪In the future♪

42:53.350 --> 42:59.070
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:00.570 --> 43:05.640
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:06.890 --> 43:12.050
♪That never expires♪

43:15.650 --> 43:20.120
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:21.120 --> 43:24.790
♪Is your name♪

43:25.290 --> 43:30.390
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:31.470 --> 43:34.690
♪At first sight♪

43:35.120 --> 43:38.400
♪The future has been determined♪

43:39.090 --> 43:44.650
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:45.750 --> 43:49.290
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:49.750 --> 43:53.690
♪Is a place♪

43:53.990 --> 43:59.550
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:00.220 --> 44:03.590
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:03.920 --> 44:07.390
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:07.920 --> 44:13.990
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
